}}

{{cmbox
| type = move
| text = type=<u>move</u> – Move, merge, and split messages and proposals such as {{tl|Category redirect}}.
}}

{{cmbox
| type = protection
| text = type=<u>protection</u> – Protection templates such as {{tl|pp}} when shown on a category page.
}}

